.TH d2b-clipboard-arm 1 1970-01-01 d2b "d2b CLI"
.SH NAME
arm \- Open the picker and request paste replay for the focused target
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBarm\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-human\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Open the picker and request paste replay for the focused target.
.PP
Opens the d2b\-clip\-picker, waits for a selection, then asks d2b\-clipd to publish the selected payload and trigger paste replay. Requires d2b\-clipd to be running.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Emit a structured JSON envelope
.TP
\fB\-\-human\fR
Emit a human\-readable status line
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
